Privacy Policy for [Desert Sniper FPS 3D Shooter Game]
Desert Sniper is an FPS 3D shooter game. The purpose of this Privacy Policy is to inform you of our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information that you may provide via our app.
Information We Collect
When you use our app, we may collect personal and non-personal information from you. This may include your name, email address, device ID, IP address, in-game activity, and purchases.
How We Acquire Information
When you create an account, interact with our app, or make in-app purchases, as well as when you choose to share data through our app, we collect information.
Utilization of Obtained Information
We may use your information to enhance your gaming experience, to improve our services, to provide customer service, and to send you information about our products and services.
Information Transfer
We neither rent nor sell your personal information to third parties. Under confidentiality agreements, we may share information with third-party service providers. If required by law, we may have to share your personal information.
Data Protection
We have implemented prudent security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access and misuse. This includes encryption technologies and server infrastructure security.
User Rights
You have the right to access, modify, amend, or even delete your personal information at any time, subject to local law.
Children's Discretion
Our application is not intended for users under 13 years old. We do not knowingly collect or store the personal information of minors under 13 years of age.
Modifications to the Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Statement periodically. When we amend the content of the policy, we will notify you by publishing the revised Privacy Policy on this page. In addition, for your convenience, we will update the 'Last updated' date at the head of the policy content.
Contact Information
Do you have concerns or queries about our Privacy Policy? In that case, please get in touch via
